{"tid":1869188,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警扮UPS速遞員拘鋼珠收件人　查信用卡、Amazon紀錄　被告曾拒簽收","createTime":"2020-02-08T04:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T04:52:53.000Z","uid":36073,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c04bd2c59ec31a84605fb87c3ef7a53d24604eca","tid":1869188,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:52:53.000Z","msg":"立場報道2020/1/22 &mdash; 13:06<br />\n<br />\n海關早前截查藏有投射器及金屬彈珠的包裹，警方即派員喬裝 UPS 速遞員，在被告拒絕簽收包裹的情況下，警於交收時將人拘捕， 24 歲男文員被控一項「企圖管有攻擊性武器」罪，今（22日）在粉嶺裁判法院再訊，暫毋須答辯。案件押後4月1日再訊，以待進一步調查，包括調查信用卡付款紀錄、電話通話紀錄等，及向網上購物平台Amazon索取相關紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n署理主任裁判官蘇文隆質疑，警方是是否已取得搜查令檢驗被告的電話，控方回應指，已取得搜令，並已將被告的電話送檢。<br />\n<br />\n被告獲准以原有條件保釋，包括以現金 1 萬元擔保，不准離港、須每晚到警署報到，以及每晚 10 時至翌日早上 5 時宵禁。<br />\n<br />\n被告鄧力豪（24歲，老人院兼職文員）被控於去年 12 月 9 日，在大埔太和路 12 號近太和邨麗和樓麥當勞餐廳外企圖管有攻擊性武器，即一套投射器及 200 粒金屬彈珠，意圖將其作非法用途使用。<br />\n<br />\n控方案情指，海關於機場截停涉案包裹，並通知警方，包裹上亦顯示被告的姓名及電話，警方隨後派員喬裝 UPS 速遞員，聯絡收件人（即被告），並約在案發的麥當勞餐廳。被告曾要求喬裝警員出示員工證，但警員聲稱其員工證遺漏在貨車，被告拒絕簽收，但最終仍被捕。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：FLCC5361/2019<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E6%89%AE%E9%80%9F%E9%81%9E%E5%93%A1%E6%8B%98%E9%8B%BC%E7%8F%A0%E6%94%B6%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%BA-%E6%9F%A5%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%A1-amazon%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E6%9B%BE%E6%8B%92%E7%B0%BD%E6%94%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2589%25AE%25E9%2580%259F%25E9%2581%259E%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258B%2598%25E9%258B%25BC%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%2594%25B6%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%259F%25A5%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%258D%25A1-amazon%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E6%2594%25B6%2F&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOnobfi2nm8u4SjNJtTZF4Nk%3D&h=5fe37474\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2589%25AE%25E9%2580%259F%25E9%2581%259E%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258B%2598%25E9%258B%25BC%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%2594%25B6%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%259F%25A5%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%258D%25A1-amazon%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E6%2594%25B6%2F&h=cdf7d4d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E6%89%AE%E9%80%9F%E9%81%9E%E5%93%A1%E6%8B%98%E9%8B%BC%E7%8F%A0%E6%94%B6%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%BA-%E6%9F%A5%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%A1-amazon%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E6%9B%BE%E6%8B%92%E7%B0%BD%E6%94%B6/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUPS制服：<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.supplychaindigital.com/sites/default/files/styles/slider_detail/public/bizclik-drupal-prod/topic/image/UPS.jpg?itok=-UWFJj5z\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.supplychaindigital.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fslider_detail%2Fpublic%2Fbizclik-drupal-prod%2Ftopic%2Fimage%2FUPS.jpg%3Fitok%3D-UWFJj5z&h=174eb737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港版UPS冇圖，不過比上圖深色啲，幾似監倉制服，狗要扮都容易"}]}